{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":920,"text":"I was born and raised in Sierra Leone,"},{"time":5126,"text":"a small and very beautiful country"},{"time":7371,"text":"in West Africa,"},{"time":9076,"text":"a country rich both in physical resources"},{"time":11980,"text":"and creative talent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14312,"text":"However, Sierra Leone is infamous"},{"time":16274,"text":"for a decade-long rebel war in the '90s"},{"time":18688,"text":"when entire villages were burnt down."},{"time":21778,"text":"An estimated 8,000 men, women and children"},{"time":25990,"text":"had their arms and legs amputated during this time."},{"time":30256,"text":"As my family and I ran for safety"},{"time":33240,"text":"when I was about 12 from one of those attacks,"},{"time":35932,"text":"I resolved that I would do everything I could"},{"time":39364,"text":"to ensure that my own children"},{"time":41644,"text":"would not go through the \nsame experiences we had."},{"time":45030,"text":"They would, in fact, be part of a Sierra Leone"},{"time":47644,"text":"where war and amputation"},{"time":50132,"text":"were no longer a strategy for gaining power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54838,"text":"As I watched people who I knew, loved ones,"},{"time":58571,"text":"recover from this devastation,"},{"time":60462,"text":"one thing that deeply troubled me"},{"time":63126,"text":"was that many of the amputees in the country"},{"time":65630,"text":"would not use their prostheses."},{"time":67686,"text":"The reason, I would come to find out,"},{"time":69642,"text":"was that their prosthetic sockets"},{"time":71977,"text":"were painful because they did not fit well."},{"time":77437,"text":"The prosthetic socket is the part"},{"time":79623,"text":"in which the amputee inserts their residual limb,"},{"time":83019,"text":"and which connects to the prosthetic ankle."},{"time":85299,"text":"Even in the developed world,"},{"time":87037,"text":"it takes a period of three weeks to often years"},{"time":90529,"text":"for a patient to get a comfortable socket, if ever."},{"time":94791,"text":"Prosthetists still use conventional processes"},{"time":97673,"text":"like molding and casting"},{"time":100029,"text":"to create single-material prosthetic sockets."},{"time":103747,"text":"Such sockets often leave intolerable amounts"},{"time":106535,"text":"of pressure on the limbs of the patient,"},{"time":109363,"text":"leaving them with pressure sores and blisters."},{"time":113663,"text":"It does not matter"},{"time":115775,"text":"how powerful your prosthetic ankle is."},{"time":118997,"text":"If your prosthetic socket is uncomfortable,"},{"time":121693,"text":"you will not use your leg,"},{"time":123265,"text":"and that is just simply unacceptable in our age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127145,"text":"So one day, when I met professor Hugh Herr"},{"time":129565,"text":"about two and a half years ago,"},{"time":131090,"text":"and he asked me if I knew \nhow to solve this problem,"},{"time":133577,"text":"I said, \"No, not yet,"},{"time":135677,"text":"but I would love to figure it out.\""},{"time":138287,"text":"And so, for my Ph.D. at the MIT Media Lab,"},{"time":141577,"text":"I designed custom prosthetic sockets"},{"time":144470,"text":"quickly and cheaply"},{"time":147377,"text":"that are more comfortable"},{"time":149232,"text":"than conventional prostheses."},{"time":152229,"text":"I used magnetic resonance imaging"},{"time":154471,"text":"to capture the actual shape of the patient's anatomy,"},{"time":158360,"text":"then use finite element modeling to better predict"},{"time":161464,"text":"the internal stresses and strains"},{"time":163407,"text":"on the normal forces,"},{"time":165405,"text":"and then create a prosthetic socket for manufacture."},{"time":170018,"text":"We use a 3D printer to create"},{"time":173432,"text":"a multi-material prosthetic socket"},{"time":177248,"text":"which relieves pressure where needed"},{"time":179714,"text":"on the anatomy of the patient."},{"time":183246,"text":"In short, we're using data"},{"time":186177,"text":"to make novel sockets quickly and cheaply."},{"time":189976,"text":"In a recent trial we just wrapped up"},{"time":191772,"text":"at the Media Lab,"},{"time":193534,"text":"one of our patients, a U.S. veteran"},{"time":196044,"text":"who has been an amputee for about 20 years"},{"time":198970,"text":"and worn dozens of legs,"},{"time":202052,"text":"said of one of our printed parts,"},{"time":206140,"text":"\"It's so soft, it's like walking on pillows,"},{"time":209544,"text":"and it's effing sexy.\""},{"time":212480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216198,"text":"Disability in our age"},{"time":219474,"text":"should not prevent anyone"},{"time":221107,"text":"from living meaningful lives."},{"time":223970,"text":"My hope and desire is that the tools and processes"},{"time":227313,"text":"we develop in our research group"},{"time":229311,"text":"can be used to bring highly functional prostheses"},{"time":232249,"text":"to those who need them."},{"time":234540,"text":"For me, a place to begin healing the souls"},{"time":239991,"text":"of those affected by war and disease"},{"time":243880,"text":"is by creating comfortable and affordable interfaces"},{"time":247629,"text":"for their bodies."},{"time":249585,"text":"Whether it's in Sierra Leone or in Boston,"},{"time":252813,"text":"I hope this not only restores"},{"time":256419,"text":"but indeed transforms their\nsense of human potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259680,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262591,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}